Rating: 3
This had great flavor, but despite the fact that I made it a day in advance and refrigerated it, it was still very liquidy. Next time I'll use 1/2 the chicken stock and slightly less wine. Also, the baguette slices baked for less than 15 minutes, but were very easy to do using an olive oil sprayer such as a "Misto."

